# vcs
.git
.gitignore

# node / next build artifacts (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# OS junk
**/.DS_Store

# tests + reports (not shipped in production image)
**/tests
**/playwright.config.ts
**/playwright-report
**/test-results

# secrets / env files (compose injects env at runtime via env_file)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# editor / docs / compose
**/.claude
**/CLAUDE.md
**/README.md
docker-compose.yml

# runtime state
**/leads.json

# stray junk
**/from preloaded import *.py
